thread.title: Lisa Collis
thread.title_full: Paper Divas reviewed by Lisa Collis

author: Lisa Collis
title: Lisa Collis
text:
I ordered my engagement invites from PaperDivas and paid the extra $20.00 to have it customized to my tastes.
Saffron, who I was dealing was lovely and happily kept updating the proof with my numerous changes I kept making, they were also happy to offer their own opinion when I asked for their thoughts!
Perfect customer service! I wouldn't hesitate to use again and again!
